rheating%20components%20or%20pressure%20leaks%2C%20before%20they%20escalate.%20Sensors%20collect%20performance%20data%20from%20equipment%2C%20and%20software%20then%20analyzes%20that%20data%20to%20pinpoint%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20need%20for%20the%20technology%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%3A%20Fortune%20Business%20Insights%20projects%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fortunebusinessinsights.com%2Fpredictive-maintenance-market-102104%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20market%20for%20predictive%20maintenance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20climb%20by%2026.5%25%20a%20year%2C%20reaching%20%2470.73%20billion%20by%202032.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20AI%20comes%20in.%20Advancements%20in%20AI%2C%20including%20generative%20AI%20and%20AI-powered%20robotics%2C%20could%20contribute%20to%20that%20growth.%20As%20AI%20capabilities%20evolve%2C%20manufacturers%20are%20integrating%20advanced%20algorithms%20into%20their%20maintenance%20systems%2C%20betting%20that%20smarter%2C%20faster%20predictions%20will%20improve%20business%20operations%20and%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20if%20growing%20pains%20don't%20get%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b413221-585b-4d6d-959a-308a5201f8b2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20and%20robots%20are%20enhancing%20predictive%20maintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EManufacturers'%20older%20systems%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20identify%20potential%20machinery%20breakdowns%20often%20overwhelm%20maintenance%20teams%20with%20false%20alarms%2C%20triggering%20unnecessary%20part%20replacements%20and%20wasted%20labor.%20Now%2C%20some%20startups%20such%20as%20Aquant%20are%20banking%20on%20AI%20to%20spot%20issues%20both%20faster%20and%20more%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAquant%20said%20its%20AI-powered%20algorithms%20can%20analyze%20past%20maintenance%20data%20to%20determine%20whether%20a%20maintenance%20action%20is%20necessary.%20For%20example%2C%20cross-referencing%20technicians'%20notes%20and%20industry%20benchmarks%20can%20help%20identify%20redundancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20platform%20then%20analyzes%20machines'%20live%20sensor%20data%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20vibrations%2C%20sounds%2C%20and%20temperature%20shifts%20%E2%80%94%20alongside%20historical%20records%20from%20customer%20relationship%20management%20systems%20and%20other%20information%20repositories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProprietary%20algorithms%20sort%20through%20the%20information%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20the%20needle%20in%20the%20haystack%26quot%3B%20and%20diagnose%20issues%20that%20need%20addressing%20as%20well%20as%20the%20causes%2C%20said%20Assaf%20Melochna%2C%20Aquant's%20president%20and%20cofounder.%20The%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20also%20designed%20to%20filter%20out%20false%20positives%2C%20then%20recommends%20specific%20actions%2C%20such%20as%20shutting%20down%20the%20machine%2C%20to%20prevent%20failure%2C%20Melochna%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20factory%20machinery%20components%20that%20affect%20uptime%2C%20Aquant%20says%20its%20AI%20platform%20is%20helping%20clients%20such%20as%20Coca-Cola%2C%20HP%2C%20and%20Hologic%20cut%20downtime%20and%20avoid%20unnecessary%20repairs%2C%20saving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiscover.aquant.ai%2Fservice-benchmark-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20to%2023%25%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20service%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20also%20make%20inspections%20safer.%20Gecko%20Robotics%20builds%20wall-climbing%20robots%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20robot%20dogs%20equipped%20with%20ultrasonic%20sensors%2C%20high-resolution%20cameras%2C%20and%20light%20detection%20and%20ranging%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gecko%20robotics%20technology%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e5be6c6ad288d14809133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGecko's%20Toka%205%20climbing%20robot%20helps%20examine%20equipment%20and%20infrastructure.%3Cp%3ERoss%20Mantle%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20robots%20are%20designed%20to%20inspect%20critical%20infrastructure%20like%20dams%2C%20power%20plants%2C%20and%20oil%20and%20gas%20facilities%2C%20collecting%20detailed%20data%20on%20pipes%2C%20tanks%2C%20vessels%2C%20and%20other%20industrial%20equipment.%20Gecko's%20AI%20platform%2C%20Cantilever%2C%20analyzes%20the%20data%20to%20detect%20corrosion%2C%20erosion%2C%20and%20cracking%20before%20failures%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20the%20data%20obtained%20by%20the%20robots%20and%20the%20AI%20platform%20to%20analyze%20it%20helps%20give%20Gecko's%20clients%2C%20including%20Siemens%20Energy%20and%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20a%20real-time%2C%20predictive%20view%20of%20asset%20health%2C%20said%20Jake%20Loosararian%2C%20Gecko%20Robotics'%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20plan%20maintenance%20before%20problems%20escalate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c905735-1eb6-4373-ab94-3876fc6405f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerative%20AI%20is%20coming%20to%20maintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gecko%20robotics%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e5c513fe8d39283657b74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20February%2C%20Gecko%20announced%20a%20%24100%20million%20deal%20with%20NAES%2C%20a%20US%20power%20operator%2C%20to%20deploy%20its%20technologies%20across%20NAES'%20production%20facilities.%3Cp%3ERoss%20Mantle%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20are%20layering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-turning-data-relatable-conversations-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econversational%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20onto%20their%20maintenance%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202006%2C%20Waites%20Sensor%20Technologies%2C%20a%20predictive%20maintenance%20firm%2C%20has%20installed%20more%20than%20500%2C000%20vibration%20and%20temperature%20sensors%20across%20Amazon%2C%20Tesla%2C%20DHL%2C%20and%20other%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Ratterman%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Waites%20had%20more%20recently%20integrated%20large%20language%20models%20into%20its%20predictive%20systems%20to%20let%20technicians%20query%20their%20systems%20directly.%20Waites'%20LLMs%20are%20trained%20on%20machine%20manuals%2C%20repair%20history%2C%20and%20sensor%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20company's%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20devices%20like%20on-site%20computers%2C%20maintenance%20personnel%20can%20ask%20Waites'%20systems%20which%20machines%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20fail%2C%20what%20past%20repairs%20were%20needed%2C%20and%20what%20maintenance%20tasks%20should%20be%20prioritized.%20Technicians%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20can%20ask%20the%20chatbot%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20the%20most%20problematic%20pieces%20of%20equipment%3F%26quot%3B%20to%20identify%20issues%2C%20or%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20relubricate%20a%20bearing%3F%26quot%3B%20to%20find%20instructions%20in%20a%20machine's%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20simplifying%20access%20to%20maintenance%20insights%2C%20LLMs%20can%20help%20teams%20make%20faster%2C%20data-driven%20decisions%20without%20needing%20to%20dig%20through%20complicated%20dashboards%20or%20reports%2C%20Ratterman%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20advancements%20in%20AI%2C%20predictive%20maintenance%20is%20now%20evolving%20into%20prescriptive%20maintenance%2C%20Kevin%20Tucker%2C%20an%20advisory%20practice%20lead%20at%20Info-Tech%20Research%20Group%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20predictive%20maintenance%20identifies%20a%20problem%2C%20prescriptive%20maintenance%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20to%20do%20to%20solve%20that%20particular%20issue.%20The%20more%20data%20predictive%20maintenance%20systems%20capture%20and%20analyze%2C%20the%20more%20accurate%20their%20predictions%20become%2C%20enhancing%20their%20abilities%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20like%20following%20your%20GPS%20in%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said%2C%20underscoring%20the%20potential%20for%20prescriptive%20maintenance%20to%20act%20as%20a%20trusted%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f91788c-9a2a-468b-9869-7481b2158ed7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpfront%20costs%20and%20fears%20around%20AI%20can%20hinder%20adoption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gecko%20robotics%20offices%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e5ca5c6ad288d14809173%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGecko's%20CEO%20said%20deploying%20new%20tech%20can%20easily%20cut%20into%20companies'%20budgets.%3Cp%3ERoss%20Mantle%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20has%20upsides%2C%20AI-driven%20predictive%20maintenance%20isn't%20easy%20to%20implement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20hurdle%20is%20cost.%20Installing%20smart%20sensors%2C%20integrating%20AI%20platforms%2C%20and%20upgrading%20legacy%20equipment%20requires%20major%20upfront%20investments%2C%20said%20Jorge%20Izquierdo%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20market%20development%20at%20The%20Association%20for%20Packaging%20and%20Processing%20Technologies%2C%20a%20trade%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIzquierdo%20called%20predictive%20systems%20the%20%26quot%3Blowest%20hanging%20fruit%26quot%3B%20for%20smart%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20packaging%20industry%2C%20but%20Tucker%20said%20incorporating%20new%20technologies%20into%20legacy%20systems%20might%20be%20hard%20to%20prioritize.%20After%20all%2C%20returns%20on%20investment%20aren't%20immediate%2C%20and%20system%20complexities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20data%20silos%20and%20the%20different%20softwares%20manufacturers%20use%20across%20the%20business%20%E2%80%94%20could%20make%20integration%20even%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20probably%20going%20to%20get%20your%20return%20on%20investment%20in%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20years%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoosararian%20emphasized%20that%20it's%20tough%20for%20companies%2C%20especially%20those%20running%20on%20tight%20budgets%2C%20to%20allocate%20resources%20toward%20implementing%20new%20technology%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20%26quot%3BInnovation%20budgets%20run%20out%20pretty%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkforce%20skills%20gaps%20pose%20another%20roadblock.%20Predictive%20maintenance%20demands%20new%20expertise%20in%20data%20analysis%20and%20AI%20tools%20management%20%E2%80%94%20skills%20that%20many%20traditional%20maintenance%20teams%20don't%20have%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prevent-employee-skepticism-push-back-gen-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emay%20be%20resistant%20to%20learn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20resistance%20is%20compounded%20by%20the%20concern%20that%20predictive%20maintenance%20systems%2C%20especially%20with%20advanced%20AI%20capabilities%2C%20may%20replace%20maintenance%20technicians'%20and%20inspectors'%20jobs.%20But%20some%20manufacturing%20leaders%20say%20the%20technology%20can%20support%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20maintenance%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraig%20Malloy%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Arix%20Technologies%2C%20a%20company%20behind%20robotic%20and%20AI%20systems%20that%20detect%20corrosion%20in%20industrial%20pipes%2C%20said%20its%20AI%20tools%20help%20free%20up%20time%20for%20maintenance%20personnel%20to%20focus%20on%20decision-making%20and%20long-term%20planning.%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20smarter%2C%20safer%2C%20more%20effective%20inspections%20%E2%80%94%20not%20fewer%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Malloy%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoosararian%20added%20that%20arming%20the%20workforce%20with%20AI%20tools%20can%20be