'd%20rather%20be%20doing%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-meta-product-manager-grow-career-uber-amazon-meta-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPMs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20designing%20a%20better-working%20tool%20or%20developing%20a%20new%20product%20for%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20ThriveAI%20comes%20in%3A%20the%20startup's%20AI%20agents%20act%20as%20junior%20product%20managers%20that%20work%20alongside%20their%20human%20counterparts%20and%20take%20over%20the%20grunt%20work%20that%20keeps%20more%20senior%20product%20managers%20preoccupied%20from%20completing%20high-value%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThriveAI's%20tech%20integrates%20into%20Slack%20and%20Microsoft%20Teams%2C%20flags%20issues%2C%20and%20synthesizes%20and%20catalogues%20data.%20Human%20PMs%20can%20delegate%20work%20to%20ThriveAI%20agents%2C%20the%20same%20way%20they'd%20interact%20with%20any%20human%20junior%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDhanuka%2C%20ThriveAI's%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20employees%20at%20the%20startup%20are%20using%20tools%20internally%20like%20AI%20code%20editor%20startup%20Cursor%20and%20that%20they%20recently%20spun%20up%20a%20dev%20agent%20that%20takes%20Slack%20requests%20and%20makes%20code%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThriveAI's%20pre-seed%20funding%20round%20will%20go%20toward%20training%20the%20AI%20agents%20to%20complete%20additional%20PM-related%20tasks%20at%20a%20high%20level%2C%20Dhanuka%20said.%20Since%20the%20PM%20role%20is%20incredibly%20broad%20and%20can%20span%20from%20anything%20including%20analyzing%20user%20feedback%20to%20monitoring%20metric%2C%20coordinating%20with%20teams%2C%20and%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20marketing%2C%20building%20out%20the%20tech's%20capabilities%20is%20the%20number%20one%20goal%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20selective%20about%20where%20we%20go%20deeper%2C%20prioritizing%20reliability%20over%20novelty%2C%20because%20the%20goal%20is%20t