0I%20have%20to%20finish%20during%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20no%20timing%20set%20for%20any%20of%20the%20tasks.%20I%20was%20someone%20who%20had%20a%20schedule%20for%20everything%20but%20now%20I%20have%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20not%20having%20a%20schedule%20and%20that%20it%20is%20all%20about%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20demands.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20three%20months%2C%20this%20new%20mother%20has%20learned%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20lessons%20of%20all%20%E2%80%94%20that%20motherhood%20rarely%20goes%20by%20the%20book.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20show%20up%20is%20simply%20to%20flow%20with%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarly%20to%20rise%2C%20last%20to%20sleep%3A%20how%20mothers%20made%20it%20work%2040%20years%20ago%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20smartphones%20to%20set%20reminders.%3Cbr%3ENo%20appliances%20to%20make%20cooking%20easier.%3Cbr%3ENo%20washing%20machines%20to%20lighten%20the%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20daily%20life%20looked%20like%20for%20Sai%20Chitra%20Venkatesh%20and%20Bhavani%20Krishnamurthy%20when%20they%20became%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99660%2Fincredible-mother-nurtures-33-children-tulsi-parihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emothers%20in%20the%201980s%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20into%20the%20same%20home%2C%20Bhavani%20(65)%20and%20Chitra%20(55)%20say%20living%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20made%20everything%20manageable%20%E2%80%94%20even%20joyful.%20It%20gave%20them%20the%20support%2C%20reassurance%2C%20and%20shared%20strength%20that%20every%20new%20mother%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-sisters%20settled%20in%20for%20a%20nostalgic%20chat%20with%20us%2C%20taking%20a%20warm%2C%20honest%20walk%20down%20memory%20lane%20%E2%80%94%20back%20to%20the%20days%20when%20motherhood%20looked%20very%20different%2C%20yet%20felt%20just%20as%20c