20to%20love%20about%20San%20Juan.%3Cp%3EMariette%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20visiting%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20for%20its%20balance%20of%20culture%2C%20stunning%20landscapes%2C%20and%20activities.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20city%20truly%20has%20something%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20what%20kind%20of%20trip%20you're%20looking%20for%2C%20you%20can%20relax%20at%20a%20beachfront%20resort%20for%20a%20few%20days%20or%20salsa%20dance%20in%20Old%20San%20Juan%20until%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-favorite-place-to-travel-without-us-passport-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747141321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681505ea3fe8d3928364cb9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-favorite-place-to-travel-without-us-passport-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20been%20on%20almost%2020%20girls'%20trips%20to%20places%20like%20Montreal%2C%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20and%20Curacao.%20My%20favorite%20destination%20has%20great%20food%20and%20beautiful%20beaches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mariette%20Williams)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A126%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-favorite-place-to-travel-without-us-passport-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%246%20billion%20Commure%20was%20just%20ordered%20to%20stop%20selling%20a%20hot%20healthtech%20product%20in%20its%20latest%20legal%20challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225185%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Athelas%20CEO%20Tanay%20Tandon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6818c9aec6ad288d147ffef0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAthelas%20CEO%20Tanay%20Tandon%2C%20pictured%2C%20co-founded%20the%20remote%20patient%20monitoring%20startup%20with%20Deepika%20Bodapati.%3Cp%3EAthelas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20court%20just%20ordered%20healthcare%20startup%20Commure%20to%20stop%20selling%20its%20hospital%20panic%20buttons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECommure%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20tech%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%246%20billion%20startup%20now%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20market%20its%20Strongline%20Pro%20product%20or%20get%20new%20customers%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20injunction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%246%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-weirdest-startup-commure-blank-check-general-catalyst-hemant-taneja-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20startup%20Commure%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20stop%20making%20one%20of%20its%20most%20historically%20successful%20products%20in%20a%20legal%20face-off%20with%20the%20tech's%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommure%2C%20the%20startup%20cofounded%20by%20General%20Catalyst%20CEO%20Hemant%20Taneja%20and%20incubated%20by%20the%20VC%20firm%2C%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20legal%20turmoil%20for%20over%20a%20year%20with%20the%20makers%20of%20its%20former%20workplace%20safety%20tech%2C%20Strongline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanopy%20Works%20created%20the%20technology%20behind%20Strongline%2C%20a%20wearable%20panic%20button%20for%20hospital%20staff%20that%20was%20once%20Commure's%20best-selling%20product.%20Canopy%20severed%20its%20ties%20with%20Commure%20in%202023%2C%20after%20which%20Commure%20released%20an%20%26quot%3Bupgrade%26quot%3B%20to%20Strongline%20called%20Strongline%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanopy%20alleged%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Commure%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California%20that%20Commure's%20Strongline%20Pro%20was%20a%20derivative%20of%20Canopy's%20Strongline%2C%20which%20violated%20the%20companies'%20contract.%20Now%2C%20a%20federal%20district%20court%20has%20sided%20with%20Canopy%20and%20ordered%20Commure%20to%20stop%20selling%20Strongline%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20preliminary%20injunction%2C%20filed%20on%20April%2025%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California%20and%20made%20public%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20prohibits%20Commure%20from%20distributing%20or%20marketing%20Strongline%20Pro%20to%20new%20customers%2C%20at%20least%20while%20the%20underlying%20breach%20of%20contract%20case%20proceeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20win%20for%20Canopy%2C%20which%20says%20it's%20lost%20business%20as%20hospital%20customers%20%26quot%3Bupgrade%26quot%3B%20from%20Canopy's%20Strongline%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-weirdest-startup-commure-blank-check-general-catalyst-hemant-taneja-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECommure's%20Strongline%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Strongline's%20business%20was%20Commure's%20sole%20growing%20revenue%20source%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20%246%20billion%20merger%20with%20fellow%20General%20Catalyst%20portfolio%20company%20Athelas%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20in%20September.%20It's%20unclear%20how%20much%20revenue%20Strongline%20Pro%20now%20contributes%20to%20Commure%20or%20how%20much%20that%20revenue%20could%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20injunction%20validates%20the%20years%20of%20dedicated%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20significant%20investment%20Canopy%20has%20poured%20into%20its%20unique%20healthcare%20safety%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20A%20Canopy%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20ruling%20provides%20certainty%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20confirming%20they%20are%20partnered%20with%20the%20creator%20of%20this%20technology%20and%20can%20trust%20the%20integrity%20and%20performance%20of%20the%20Canopy%20system%20safeguarding%20their%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommure%20has%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20delay%20the%20injunction's%20enforcement.%20In%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Commure%20SVP%20and%20General%20Manager%20Dan%20Warner%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20to%20overturn%20the%20injunction%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20law%20and%20facts%20are%20firmly%20on%20Commure's%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Commure%20developed%20Strongline%20Pro%20entirely%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Commure%20has%20expanded%20well%20beyond%20its%20workplace%20safety%20product%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20The%20startup%20has%20signaled%20its%20intentions%20to%20dig%20deeper%20into%20healthcare%20AI%20following%20its%20acquisition%20of%20revenue%20cycle%20management%20company%20Athelas%2C%20buying%20ambient%20scribing%20company%20Augmedix%20in%20July%202024%20for%20%24139%20million%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20scooping%20up%20another%20General%20Catalyst%20portfolio%20company%2C%20AI-powered%20care%20coordination%20platform%20Memora%20Health%2C%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%20is%20also%20closing%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20Akron%2C%20Ohio-based%20health%20system%20Summa%20Health.%20The%20firm%20has%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20integrate%20healthcare%20technology%20into%20the%20hospitals'%20operations%2C%20an%20endeavor%20that%20would%20likely%20include%20Commure's%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273d73c31-c797-4cad-aace-d8b38e17858e%5C%22%3ECommure's%20battle%20with%20Canopy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECommure%20and%20Canopy%20created%20their%20first%20agreement%20to%20make%20Commure%20a%20reseller%20of%20Canopy's%20technology%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Commure%20bought%20the%20rights%20to%20white-label%20and%20sell%20Strongline's%20wearable%20panic%20buttons%20for%20hospital%20staff.%20Canopy%20Works%2C%20then%20known%20as%20SMP%20Labs%2C%20remained%20a%20separate%20company%20and%20retained%20ownership%20of%20the%20intellectual%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20quickly%20escalated%20after%20the%20acquisition.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20Commure%20sued%20Canopy%20when%20the%20company%20tried%20to%20terminate%20its%20partnership%20with%20Commure.%20Canopy%20had%20cited%20delayed%20payments%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20breaking%20away%20from%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20lawsuit%20was%20dismissed%20and%20later%20settled%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20was%20done.%20By%20December%202023%2C%20Canopy%20spun%20out%20for%20good%20as%20a%20new%20company%20to%20sell%20its%20safety%20technology%20directly%20to%20health%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommure%20moved%20quickly%20to%20rebuild%20its%20workplace%20safety%20business%2C%20launching%20Strongline%20Pro%20just%20days%20after%20Canopy's%20debut.%20Commure%20positioned%20Strongline%20Pro%20as%20a%20successor%20to%20the%20original%20Strongline%20product%2C%20although%20filings%20with%20federal%20regulators%20showed%20substantial%20similarities%20between%20the%20two%20devices%2C%20per%20BI's%20September%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommure%20holds%20that%20%26quot%3BStrongline%20Pro%20was%20developed%20independently%20by%20Commure%20without%20using%20any%20information%20from%20Canopy%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20Friday%20injunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Canopy's%20exodus%2C%20Commure%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Canopy%20in%20April%202024%2C%20alleging%20that%20Commure%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Strongline's%20original%20concept%20and%20that%20Canopy%20had%20violated%20its%20contractual%20obligations%20to%20provide%20its%20tech%20to%20Commure%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20Commure%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20alleged%20security%20vulnerabilities%20in%20Canopy's%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20ordered%20in%20the%20injunction%2C%20existing%20Strongline%20Pro%20customers%20can%20continue%20to%20use%20Strongline%20Pro%2C%20but%20Commure%20cannot%20upgra