he%200.3%25%20expected%20but%20more%20than%20the%20previous%200.1%25%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECore%20inflation%20held%20steady%20at%202.8%25%20over%20the%20year%20in%20April%2C%20as%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20UBS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D71029cdc4a1721399890e8b9038f3f1beb4c68eb3ee228bdf08d815b8cc0b365%26postID%3D6822678fb2c932bc4b8c467b%26postSlug%3Dinflation-april-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Feconomy%252Fwill-april-cpi-report-show-first-inflation-impacts-tariffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enote%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicted%20that%20April%20data%20would%20mark%20the%20start%20of%20the%20impacts%20of%20Trump's%20implemented%20tariffs%2C%20and%20that%20May%20through%20October%20would%20show%20larger%20impacts%20if%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-deals-list-status-talks-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariff%20effects%20haven't%20shown%20up%20much%20in%20inflation%20data%20yet.%20The%20index%20for%20new%20vehicles%20was%20unchanged%20in%20April%20after%20increasing%200.1%25%20in%20March.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20food%20index%20fell%200.1%25%2C%20the%20first%20month-over-month%20decline%20since%202020.%20Apparel%20also%20fell%20in%20April%20after%20an%20increase%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20energy%20index%20surged%200.7%25%20in%20April%20from%20March%2C%20following%20a%202.4%25%20decline.%20The%20index%20fell%203.7%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowth%20in%20the%20shelter%20index%20held%20steady%2C%20rising%204%25%20over%20the%20year%20again.%20It%20increased%200.3%25%20over%20the%20month%20after%20increasing%200.2%25%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Federal%20Open%20Market%20Committee%20members%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rates-federal-reserve-holds-steady-no-cuts-inflation-trump-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehold%20interest%20rates%20steady%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20they%20wait%20for%20more%20certainty%20around%20tariffs'%20impacts.%20CME%20FedWatch%2C%20which%20shows%20what%20traders%20think%20will%20happen%20to%20interest%20rates%2C%20showed%20before%20and%20after%20the%20inflation%20report%20a%2092%25%20chance%20that%20rates%20will%20be%20unchanged%20at%20the%20FOMC's%20next%20scheduled%20meeting%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20announced%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20on%20April%202%2C%20before%20quickly%20pausing%20many%20of%20them%20for%2090%20days.%20A%20baseline%20of%2010%25%20has%20been%20in%20effect%2C%20along%20with%20a%20145%25%20tariff%20on%20most%20imports%20from%20China%20and%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20autos%2C%20steel%2C%20and%20aluminum.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmarkets-sp500-dow-nasdaq-us-china-trade-tariff-talks-switzerland-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrade%20deal%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20key%20trade%20partner%20for%20the%20US.%20Both%20countries%20will%20cut%20rates%20by%20115%20percentage%20points%20for%2090%20days.%20Last%20week%2C%20Trump%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-announces-a-major-trade-deal-deal-with-uk-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20and%20UK%20reached%20a%20trade%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2010%25%20tariff%20is%20still%20in%20effect%2C%20but%20the%20two%20countries%20negotiated%20agreements%20on%20vehicles%2C%20steel%2C%20and%20aluminum%20from%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaroline%20Leavitt%2C%20the%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bis%20committed%20to%20the%2010%25%20baseline%20tariff%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20but%20for%20his%20trade%20negotiations%20with%20all%20other%20countries%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeiChen%20Lin%2C%20senior%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Russell%20Investments%2C%20said%20that%20businesses%20likely%20stocked%20up%20before%20Trump's%2010%25%20tariffs%2C%20which%20could%20be%20delaying%20their%20impact%20on%20inflation%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20broad%2010%25%20universal%20tariff%20doesn't%20get%20negotiated%20away%2C%20then%20eventually%20we%20will%20likely%20see%20a%20one-time%20boost%20to%20price%20levels%2C%20which%20would%20also%20translate%20into%20a%20temporary%20boost%20to%20the%20inflation%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Lin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20could%20also%20affect%20overall%20economic%20growth%20and%20the%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20large%20increases%20in%20tariffs%20that%20have%20been%20announced%20are%20sustained%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20generate%20a%20rise%20in%20inflation%2C%20a%20slowdown%20in%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20unemployment%2C%26quot%3B%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20said%20in%20a%20May%207%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20resilient%2C%20with%20a%20solid%20job%20market%20and%20inflation%20just%20above%20the%20Fed's%20target%20of%202%25.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgdp-gross-domestic-product-first-quarter-2025-recession-outlook-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReal%20gross%20domestic%20product%20shrank%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20the%20first%20time%20since%202022%2C%20but%20a%20large%20rise%20in%20imports%20that%20subtracts%20from%20growth%20contributed%20to%20that%20contraction.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapril-jobs-report-unemployment-rate-employment-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJob%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20better%20than%20expected%20in%20April%2C%20but%20still%20indicated%20a%20tougher%20job%20market%20for%20unemployed%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20said%20the%20Fed's%20policy%20is%20%26quot%3B100%20basis%20points%20less%20restrictive%20than%20it%20was%20last%20fall.%20And%20so%2C%20we%20think%20that%20leaves%20us%20in%20a%20good%20place%20to%20wait%20and%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20Please%20check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-april-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747139598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68221bbbc6ad288d1480a7dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-april-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inflation%20is%20getting%20closer%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%202%25%20target.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-april-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98No%20change%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20policy%2C%20issue%20a%20bilateral%20matter%20between%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Pak%E2%80%99%3A%20MEA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747139398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121140387%2Cimgsize-1305020.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-change-in-jk-policy-issue-a-bilateral-matter-between-india-pakistan-mea%2Farticleshow%2F1211404