d%20for%20workers%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20unorganised%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahanta%20notes.%20Yet%2C%20he%20estimates%20that%20nearly%2010%2C000%20people%20are%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20involved%20in%20bay%20leaf%20cultivation%20and%20basic%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20leading%20this%20transformation%20is%20the%20Hemtabad%20Block%2C%20now%20recognised%20as%20the%20top%20producer%20of%20the%20Bengal%20variety%20of%20bay%20leaves.%20According%20to%20Mahanta%2C%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20contributing%20to%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20is%20its%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CA%20bay%20leaf%20tree%20requires%20less%20water%20and%20low%20maintenance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20making%20it%20a%20sustainable%20option%20for%20many%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tree%20that%20keeps%20on%20giving%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20farmers%20like%20Sukumar%20Barman%20in%20West%20Bengal%20relied%20on%20traditional%20crops%20like%20paddy.%20But%20the%20returns%20were%20modest%2C%20and%20the%20effort%20was%20relentless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20paddy%20on%20one%20bigha%20of%20land%20would%20fetch%20just%20Rs%2030%2C000%E2%80%9340%2C000%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Barman.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20labour%2C%20and%20getting%20the%20harvest%20to%20market%20on%20time%20was%20another%20challenge%20altogether.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20bay%20leaf%20cultivation%20has%20become%20a%20game-changer%20for%20his%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20brought%20real%20economic%20development%20to%20our%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20the%20spice.%20The%20tree%E2%80%99s%20twigs%20are%20ground%20into%20powders%2C%20its%20leaves%20are%20used%20as%20a%20natural%20colourant%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20staple%20in%20kitchens%20across%20India%2C%20enhancing%20the%20flavour%20of%20both%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201197px)%20100vw%2C%201197px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221197%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bay%20leaves%20cultivation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923.jpeg%201197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923-300x160.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923-500x266.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923-768x409.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FSukumar-Barman-is-making-fortune-from-his-bay-leaves-garden-located-in-the-North-Dinajpur-district-2_6_11zon-1747042923-150x80.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-427126%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBay%20leaf%20cultivation%20has%20become%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Sukumar%20Barman%E2%80%99s%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20brought%20real%20economic%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Barman%20saw%20the%20rising%20demand%2C%20he%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20three%20types%20of%20bay%20leaves%20%E2%80%94%20Bengal%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Shillong.%20I%20chose%20the%20Bengaluru%20variety%20because%20it%20produces%20more%20leaves.%20He%20explains%20that%20I%20spent%20Rs%2032%2C500%20on%20saplings%2C%20each%20costing%20Rs%2050%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBay%20leaf%20trees%20are%20hardy%2C%20tall%2C%20and%20evergreen%20%E2%80%94%20ideal%20for%20the%20region.%20Once%20planted%2C%20they%20take%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20mature.%20But%20the%20reward%20is%20long-lasting%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20single%20tree%20can%20yield%2015%20to%2020%20kg%20of%20leaves%20every%20year%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Barman%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20farmers%20lease%20out%20their%20bay%20leaf%20gardens%20to%20traders%20for%20three%20years.%20In%20return%2C%20these%20traders%20handle%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20hiring%20labourers%20and%20maintaining%20the%20trees%20to%20pest%20control%2C%20harvesting%2C%20packaging%2C%20and%20even%20transportation.%20For%20farmers%20like%20Barman%2C%20it%20means%20less%20stress%2C%20more%20support%2C%20and%20a%20more%20secure%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20sapling%20to%20spice%3A%20What%20it%20takes%20to%20grow%20bay%20leaf%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBay%20leaf%20trees%20may%20look%20unassuming%2C%20but%20they%20are%20incredibly%20rewarding%20for%20those%20who%20nurture%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sapling%20grows%20to%20a%20height%20of%201.5%E2%80%932%20feet%20annually%2C%20while%20a%20tree%20can%20grow%20to%20over%2020%E2%80%9330%20feet%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sukumar%20Barman.%20%E2%80%9CA%2010-foot-tall%20tree%20can%20produce%20seven%20to%20eight%20kilograms%20of%20leaves.%20It%20grows%20well%20in%20loamy%20soil.%20The%20quality%20of%20soil%20and%20dry%20weather%20determine%20the%20size%20of%20a%20leaf%2C%20which%20is%20thick%2C%20fibrous%2C%20shiny%2C%20about%201.5%E2%80%932%20inches%20wide%2C%20and%205%E2%80%938%20inches%20long.%20It%20is%20olive%20green%2C%20dark%20green%2C%20and%20light%20brown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20harvest%20season%20runs%20from%20August%20to%20December%2C%20but%20the%20frequency%20depends%20on%20how%20quickly%20the%20leaves%20mature.%20%E2%80%9CHarvesting%20occurs%20every%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20%E2%80%94%20even%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20some%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Barman%20adds.%20Once%20plucked%2C%20the%20leaves%20are%20left%20to%20dry%20for%20three%20to%20four%20sunny%20days.%20But%20the%20monsoon%20season%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CCovering%20the%20leaves%20with%20plastic%20sheets%20becomes%20expensive%20because%20of%20the%20extra%20labour%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarman%2C%20always%20keen%20to%20maximise%20his%20yield%2C%20found%20an%20innovative%20way%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20his%20farmland.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20bay%20leaf%20plants%20grew%20four%20feet%20above%20the%20soil%2C%20I%20even%20planted%20potatoes%20and%20black%20gram%20in%20the%20space%20(8%C3%978%20feet)%20between%20trees.%20This%20helps%20fertilise%20the%20field%20and%20improves%20the%20growth%20of%20trees.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20I%20harvested%20for%20the%20first%20time%20when%20the%20trees%20were%20seven%20to%2010%20feet%20tall.%20I%20also%20do%20regular%20pruning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBay%20leaves%20are%20sorted%20into%20different%20quality%20grades%2C%20determining%20where%20they%E2%80%99re%20sent.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20quality%20leaves%20are%20spotless.%20A%20leaf%20has%20A%2C%20B%2C%20and%20C%20grades.%20The%20A-grade%20quality%20is%20exported%20to%20the%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20while%20B%20and%20C%20grades%20are%20supplied%20across%20India.%20It%20has%205%25%20GST.%20The%20dried%20leaves%20are%20packed%20in%20jute%20bags%20and%20plastic%20bags%20before%20being%20dispatched%20to%20cities%20such%20as%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20trader%20Sudeb%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20currently%20leases%2014%20bay%20leaf%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20demand%20soaring%2C%20a%20structured%20but%20informal%20system%20has%20evolved.%20Farmers%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20labour%20or%20resources%20often%20lease%20out%20their%20gardens%20through%20open%20tenders%20for%20a%20period%20of%20three%20to%20three-and-a-half%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20bidder%20gets%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sarkar.%20Once%20a%20deal%20is%20made%2C%20traders%20step%20in%2C%20bringing%20in%20skilled%20labourers%20to%20climb%20trees%20and%20harvest%20leaves%20with%20sickles.%20Women%20complete%20the%20essential%20post-harvest%20work.%20Today%2C%20North%20Dinajpur%20alone%20has%20around%20100%E2%80%93150%20such%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrading%2C%20profits%20and%20the%20challenges%20that%20come%20with%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20bay%20leaf%20farming%20brings%20in%20significant%20profits%20for%20cultivators%2C%20the%20picture%20differs%20slightly%20for%20traders%20who%20take%20on%20leased%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20pay%20Rs%201900%20per%20quintal%20labour%20cost%20for%20cutting%20twigs%2C%20leaves%2C%20stacking%2C%20and%20packing.%20Further%2C%20Rs%20700%20per%20quintal%20is%20spent%20on%20watering%20the%20trees%2C%20applying%20proper%20manure%20or%20fertiliser%2C%20and%20spraying%20insecticides%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20a%2029-year-old%20trader.%20%E2%80%9CA%20trader%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20benefit%20as%20much%20as%20a%20farmer%20does.%20With%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20tender%2C%20the%20farmer%20gets%20back%20his%20garden.%20Some%2030%20farmers%20are%20still%20maintaining%20gardens%2C%20while%20most%20of%20the%20gardens%20are%20operated%20by%20traders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBay%20leaf%20trading%20may%20be%20lucrative%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20without%20its%20challenges%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20plant%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGuarding%20the%20green%20gold%3A%20tackling%20pests%20%26amp%3B%20preserving%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20culinary%20appeal%2C%20the%20bay%20leaf%20has%20medicinal%20and%20nutritional%20benefits.%20With%20314%20calories%2C%20a%20single%20leaf%20offers%20238%25%20of%20the%20daily%20iron%20requirement%2C%2085%25%20of%20vitamin%20B-6%2C%20and%2083%25%20of%20calcium.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20rich%20in%20magnesium%2C%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20carbohydrates.%20But%20like%20any%20crop%2C%20bay%20leaf%20trees%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20pest%20attacks%20and%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommon%20ailments%20include%20leaf%20spot%2C%20dieback%2C%20blight%2C%20and%20bark%20canker.%20Harmful%20pests%20such%20as%20the%20leaf%20webber%2C%20chafer%20beetle%2C%20cinnamon%20butterfly%2C%20scale%20insects%2C%20and%20gall%20mites%20can%20cause%20considerable%20damage%20if%20not%20managed%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-97_11zon-1-1747045398.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harmful%20pests%20like%20leaf%20webbers%2C%20chafer%20beetles%2C%20cinnamon%20butterflies%2C%20scale%20insects%2C%20and%20gall%20mites%20can%20cause%20serious%20damage%20if%20not%20managed%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-9