0breath%20for%20over%2030%20minutes%2C%20but%20when%20entangled%2C%20they%20panic%2C%20use%20up%20oxygen%20faster%2C%20and%20drown.%20Arun%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20turtle%20deaths%20we%20see%20are%20due%20to%20drowning%20in%20trawl%20nets.%20The%20problem%20isn%E2%80%99t%20visible%20to%20those%20ashore%20%E2%80%94%20it%20happens%20far%20from%20sight%2C%20in%20the%20deeper%20waters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrem%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20all%20fishermen%20are%20the%20same.%20Most%20of%20us%20want%20the%20sea%20to%20flourish.%20But%20deep-sea%20trawling%20without%20following%20appropriate%20guidelines%20is%20destructive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEcological%20wisdom%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reverence%20towards%20these%20Ridley%20turtles%20isn%E2%80%99t%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20alone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20ecological%20wisdom%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20Olive%20Ridleys%20feed%20primarily%20on%20jellyfish%20and%20seaweed.%20Jellyfish%2C%20often%20seen%20as%20pests%20by%20fishermen%2C%20can%20damage%20nets%20and%20kill%20smaller%20fish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20turtles%20help%20maintain%20a%20balanced%20food%20chain.%20Where%20there%20are%20turtles%2C%20there%20is%20good%20water%20flow%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20more%20fish%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prem.%20Turtles%20are%20thus%20indicators%20of%20a%20healthy%20marine%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20sustains%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20very%20people%20often%20accused%20of%20harming%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20turtles%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20fishermen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palayam%20says.%20%E2%80%9CKutty%20Amma%20brings%20the%20fish%20with%20her.%20When%20she%20comes%20to%20lay%20eggs%2C%20the%20tiny%20fish%20get%20stuck%20to%20her%20belly.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20highlighting%20how%20this%20also%20increases%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20fishing%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20at%20the%20real%20danger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20their%20efforts%2C%20fishermen%20continue%20to%20be%20scapegoated.%20When%20images%20of%20oil-slicked%20turtles%20emerge%20after%20environmental%20disasters%2C%20the%20media%20seeks%20quick%2C%20digestible%20outrage.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20wanted%20us%20to%20say%20the%20turtle%20died%20due%20to%20the%20oil%20spill%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20said%20no%20%E2%80%94%20it%20likely%20died%20earlier.%20The%20problem%20is%20deeper%3A%20trawling%2C%20pollution%2C%20unsustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Fengal%20cyclone%20in%20November%202024%2C%20Payalam%20was%20left%20grappling%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20along%20the%20shore.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20pollution%20near%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417010%2Fsstcn-chennai-olive-ridley-conservation-decades-student-initiative-hatchery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroken%20bridge%20in%20Adyar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20so%20severe%20that%20many%20fish%20perished%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palayam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20conditions%2C%20how%20can%20we%20expect%20the%20turtles%20to%20survive%2C%20let%20alone%20lay%20their%20eggs%20peacefully%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks%2C%20his%20voice%20filled%20with%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2